This is a simple gestural mouse for the Mac OS X using a Xbox Kinect. It s based on the libfreenect and openFrameworks.

The openFrameworks addons required are --
ofxOpenCv, ofxThread, ofxVectorMath, ofxXmlSettings, ofxMSAInteractiveObject, ofxSimpleGuiToo, ofxKinect

To run the application -- 
Copy the files into the $ofx/apps/myApps/KinectMouse folder and compile and run the application using XCode